          .hex #228a43
        .color
          .sample(class='light-blue')
          .name Light blue
          .hex #0083a9

  .guide
    .content
      h2 Production
      p The Missouri flag has a proportion of 7:12. The width of the blue band around the center circle of the seal is 1/14 the width of the hoist. The diameter of the circle is 1/3 the length of the fly.
      p If resized, it must maintain these proportions.
    .visual
      img(src='/assets/images/flag-missouri-dimensions.svg')

